OL,4,G2200FGame Show Models
OL,5,     GStuart Guber leaves his
OL,6,     Gperformance-artist girlfriend to
OL,7,     Grejoin society, taking a job at a
OL,8,     Gmajor record label. Chaos begins
OL,9,     Gwhen his boss launches a bizarre
OL,10,     Gsex-themed game show.
OL,11,G2350FChildren Shouldn't Play with Dead
OL,12,     FThings
OL,13,     GA horror film with brains albeit
OL,14,     Gsemi-digested! This cult American
OL,15,     Gfavourite from the 1970s sees a
OL,16,     Gvoodoo ritual go hideously wrong,
OL,17,     Gsummoning dead children from
OL,18,     Gtheir graves to devour.
